export const questionsThree = [
	{
		id: 0,
		questionNumber: 11,
		question:
			'Alice was the first to use many new inventions, ____ sound and color.',
		answerOptions: [
			{ answerText: 'bringing', isCorrect: false },
			{ answerText: 'including', isCorrect: true },
			{ answerText: 'containing', isCorrect: false },
			{ answerText: 'supporting', isCorrect: false },
		],
	},
	{
		id: 1,
		questionNumber: 12,
		question:
			'In 1907 Alice ____ to New York where she started her own film company.',
		answerOptions: [
			{ answerText: 'moved', isCorrect: true },
			{ answerText: 'ran', isCorrect: false },
			{ answerText: 'entered', isCorrect: false },
			{ answerText: 'transported', isCorrect: false },
		],
	},
	{
		id: 2,
		questionNumber: 13,
		question: 'She was ____ successful',
		answerOptions: [
			{ answerText: 'next', isCorrect: false },
			{ answerText: 'once', isCorrect: false },
			{ answerText: 'immediately', isCorrect: true },
			{ answerText: 'recently', isCorrect: false },
		],
	},
	{
		id: 3,
		questionNumber: 14,
		question:
			'the best days of the independent New York film companies were ____.',
		answerOptions: [
			{ answerText: 'after', isCorrect: false },
			{ answerText: 'down', isCorrect: false },
			{ answerText: 'behind', isCorrect: false },
			{ answerText: 'over', isCorrect: true },
		],
	},
	{
		id: 4,
		questionNumber: 15,
		question: 'When Alice died in 1968, hardly anybody ____ her name.',
		answerOptions: [
			{ answerText: 'remembered', isCorrect: true },
			{ answerText: 'realized', isCorrect: false },
			{ answerText: 'reminded', isCorrect: false },
			{ answerText: 'repeated', isCorrect: false },
		],
	},
